Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うんざりだよね  だから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:56.68,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂々と断っちゃう　キミになりなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:57.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:01.53,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キッパリしなきゃ　嘘に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:06.60,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付きあってられないよ　狭い世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自分で見つけた　myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.50,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好きになって当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.96,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くだらないやり方蹴って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:18.93,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すべてはあたしが決める!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.35,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(I say,I say my heaven)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.85,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Driver　突進まかせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.77,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんてったって前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.58,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可能！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.72,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Don't you stop me)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛び越えて　Take it eazy,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.41,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大勝利って同感もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.31,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうなったって快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.03,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「反省会？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.40,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Get back to wild)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:40.44,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それより　さあ　急いでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:45.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれもこれも未体験　いつだってムリヤリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:49.98,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まるでまるで未経験　これからしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:54.71,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれもこれも未体験　いつだってトツゼン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:59.52,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まるでまるで未経験　それがどうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.16,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为无聊之极
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:56.68,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才必须堂堂正正地拒绝　如你一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:57.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:01.53,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须对谎话斩钉截铁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:06.60,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这不能相处的狭窄世界内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.16,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现自己　myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.50,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会喜欢上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.96,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把无聊的东西一脚踢开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:18.93,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都由我来决定！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.35,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(I say,I say my heaven)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.85,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Driver　随我冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.77,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管一切向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.58,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可能！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.72,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Don't you stop me)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来飞越　Take it eazy,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.41,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是取得大胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.31,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法阻挡的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.03,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「反省会？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.40,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Get back to wild)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:40.44,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个　来吧　加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:45.07,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个那个也还没体验　无论何时都要硬干下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:49.98,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全地没有经验　现在就去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:54.71,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个那个也还没体验　无论何时都要马上行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:59.52,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全地没有经验　那又怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:45.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}空から落ちてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:47.86,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全ての願いを乗せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:52.43,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ひとつの星にはちょっと重かったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.08,0:23:55.66,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}やっぱり何かヘンだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:58.27,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心のキミが消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:02.62,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}確かに憶えてるって言えるのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.10,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}止マレ！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.26,0:24:07.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}過去は自分のもの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.05,0:24:12.35,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}当然　誰とも取り替えたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:13.56,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}なぜなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:18.72,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}バースデイだった　私達には
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:21.69,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}出会いが生まれたときに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}初めての夢が見える
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:29.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}どうしようかって　悩んだ事も
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:33.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いま思えば笑えるほどだったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.15,0:24:37.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう忘れてた　キミを探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:45.05,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}仅仅只因从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:47.86,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}便要承担全部愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:52.43,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}对于一颗小小流星　是否有些沉重？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.08,0:23:55.66,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果然有哪里出了错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:58.27,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心中你已消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:02.62,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}「没忘掉你」这话　又要怎么说出？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.10,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}停下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.26,0:24:07.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}过去只属于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.05,0:24:12.35,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}当然不会将其交给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:13.56,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:18.72,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}生日那一天　大家在此处相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:21.69,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但在那天的初梦前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.07,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我们早已相知相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:29.05,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}之前那不知如何是好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:33.02,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}此刻回想　却是那般可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.15,0:24:37.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}已经忘了吗　那来找你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个慵懒  而又正常到了极点的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂兰盆会后的盛夏的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视中正在播放的  是跟我一点关系都没有的同县选手的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于对弱者的同情心  我不由得支持着正处于落后的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这时手机却大声嚷嚷了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春日啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两点整全员在车站前集合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻描淡写地挂断了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么就知道我今天很闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我可也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  虽说我什么计划也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你说了  带一套泳装骑车过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.21,0:01:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  带上足够的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上  Over～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:14.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打手现正悠闲地跑向三垒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:17.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投手铃木  在投手丘上一副崩溃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:20.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是惨不忍睹的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:21.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凄惨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人向投手铃木发出嘘声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:32.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就是8：0了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:35.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛进入了艰巨的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.44,staffbiaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fn方正黑体_GBK\pos(235,294)\fs27\an5}Endless Eight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.44,staffbiaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fn方正黑体_GBK\pos(235,370)\an5}漫无止境的八月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虚！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多拿点干劲出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让本团长等你  你以为自己是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要惩罚啦  惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就提前了15分钟来  为什么每次都是最后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  全都到齐了  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉  你就载实玖瑠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和有希坐阿虚后面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且问一句  去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天当然要有夏天的样子  要做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的时间可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:04:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在就要行动  在这个只有一次的高一的暑假里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的时间啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这消毒液的气味  真给人一种实在的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来～啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（禁止跳水  危险！）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧过来  水温温的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就看不见到处贴的那些禁止跳水的文字说明么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很让人欣慰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得  凉宫同学也学会了有常识性的娱乐方法了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打个电话过来  单方面地说好就挂的邀请方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不能说得上是常识性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  笑得那么开心的凉宫同学  是不会做什么震动这个世界的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心  自从上次合宿以来  也没引起过什么让人注目的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这会儿  对凉宫同学而言也好  对我们来说也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就是和平的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是  实玖瑠亲手做的三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再吃一块炸鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  给我倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  非常和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是市民泳池  倒是个更适合平民泳池这名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  实玖瑠你在干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种过暑假的方法倒也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就是我的团员们  说什么都会听的  所以随便吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着考虑了下今后的活动计划  如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样来度过已经所剩无几的暑假的计划表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  暑假只剩下两周了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得还有很多事情没做呢  要一起都做完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在暑假不能不做的事情…么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏期合宿  游泳池  盆舞  烟花汇演  打工  天体观测…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个表上的东西要在两周之内都做完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的想要做的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  我想捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天开始实行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有什么地方明天会跳盆舞么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烟花汇演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少查过了再给我实行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查吧  回头联系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  别忘了捞金鱼哦  这可是实玖瑠的强烈要求哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是我付钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你迟到了  这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天可别让人等了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  现在开始每天都玩么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  将我的懒觉夺走的又是春日打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到跳盆舞的会场了  时间是今晚  地点是市民运动场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏她能时机正好地找到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中正半怀佩服时  春日说出了这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去买浴衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠和有希都说没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买一整套的话就会便宜  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日擅自为朝比奈学姐和长门挑选了以后  毫不客气地冲进了试衣间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可相当花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期间频遭女性顾客冷眼  我们等了大约一小时  三个人终于都换好出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都非常合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦  是我给挑选的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我挑的  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会看走眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  这是在春日强行加上的服装中最顶级的货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  超合适  这个给YES
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（YESだね：捏自Brain Power(机动神脑)的台词）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是这个国家的古典民俗衣着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然胸口有点难受  不过好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就准备好了  那么出发吧  去盆舞会场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过盆舞啊  感觉好像很久没有看到过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  实玖瑠  你想要玩的捞金鱼也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捞个痛快吧  黑色凸眼金鱼可是加200分的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去玩吧  来比比看能捞多少条如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我PASS  比起那个我还是对食物有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门你觉得如何  要吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那种东西有兴趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13条  虽然是大丰收但我不需要那么多  就只要了一条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是完全捞不起来  捞金鱼好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  正常人是捞不了那么多的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有诀窍的话就很简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有希  那个面具是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗…不过为什么要这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是波长相合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为是宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不管了  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一块还没转过  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要玩么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃一个的话没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  盆舞也差不多跳完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来玩烟花吧  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花…么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得穿这身  今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对  对面的店里就有卖的  就去河边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柿崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（此处捏自「超时空要塞Macross」剧场版的柿崎机(VF-1A)）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盆舞  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天是捉昆虫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  虽说玩也没问题  你暑假作业做完了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说一点也没有动的我说这话有点那啥就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  那种程度的作业有三天不就全部做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我七月就解决掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种麻烦事就得事先赶紧收拾了  再毫无后顾之忧地玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是正确的享受暑假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种家伙脑子这么好  上天对于人的参数调整还真是随便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  明天去捉昆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到的虫子最多的那个人…  这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把团长的权力让给他一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣呢  只要是虫子的话什么都可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…只能抓蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这就是SOS团内部的捉蝉大战  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只多抓了一只也算赢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了祈雨  我把晴天娃娃用五寸钉刺着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到来的却是万里无云的好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉也为今年夏天最热的一天而雀跃不已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  蝉能够拿来吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许弄成天妇罗会是极品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我有时会想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天妇罗会不会只是外面一层面衣好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  那蝉也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉！快向全国的天妇罗店道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让青春年华的高中生拿着虫网与笼子聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  没有虫网的话怎么抓蝉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是问那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们开始了  优胜者可以当一天的团长！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没在听…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的想赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  捕蝉的话  小学不都试过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊  尽力而行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经抓到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是蝉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海…海格力斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:36.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大力神独角仙(D.hercules)，胸部有大而光滑的角）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公布结果！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠一只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希四只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉七只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚九只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后最高纪录是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你不用说都知道是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！十二只！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  团长之座一天都让不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真是可惜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会真的想把它们做成天妇罗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你想吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么成我要吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  还是要有放生的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放它们一条生路  以后说不定会来报恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快回山里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:15:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是说得好听  但你这只是单方面的捕捉后放生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是接着的下一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日不知从何处找来了兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还难得为我们争取了机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地超市的纪念促销宣传活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作内容是吸引顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…连我都非得装成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是暑假的兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有别的做法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且春日只是在一旁凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下来与她的日薪要是一样的话  绝对要暴动的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于能明白脱皮后蛇的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  真是一个好例子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长大叔也谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个外套就是工钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在实玖瑠的份上说送给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只青蛙要放在社团室里当作纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  你想什么时候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我许可的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳池  盂兰盆节  捕虫  兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后春日进行的就是天体观测
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这就是这个年代的望远镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与开普勒时代的没什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得相差很远…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是买来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我小时候的兴趣就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看见木星卫星的时候真的十分激动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是火星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不希望它存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼一样的怪物蜿蜒地计划着征服地球的图像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要说好话我也不觉得有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是十分友好的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在地下的大空洞偷偷地生活着的害羞人种
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让地球人感到吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脑内的火星人到底有多么文雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来找UFO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在卫星轨道上  一定有异星人的先遣队在待机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  实玖瑠也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呃…UFO  UFO…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假还未结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日接着要做的是——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到击球中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早看见甲子园的新闻我就想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能只满足于那些杂牌的棒球比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们SOS团要建成以全国为目标的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能量到底是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是细胞内的线粒体与常人不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些能量能为世人用上一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后  谁也不能阻止春日定下的定额消耗态势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不停地跟着行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去了真正的烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也将砰砰地射上高空\N又碰碰地绽放的烟花观赏到满足为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另一天  我们则在县边境的河边参加钓虾虎鱼大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  实玖瑠  竿子竿子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧  我会拿回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是固定节目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但应该没有人真会去玩的试胆大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看了只有宣传非常像那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但内容大家都心知肚明的大制作电影的联播
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完全是淡季的会漂来水母的海滩上进行海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到所有人都达到全清才能离开的保龄球惩罚游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑战喉咙极限的长时间耐久卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至觉得包括了很多与夏天无关的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我们在这两周内玩到再起不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是8月30日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课题都完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀唉呀  总算顺利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…嗯  也就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还有什么想做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好  这个夏天都干了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四处游玩  也穿上了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉也抓了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到这里为止吧  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这家伙还有什么遗憾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就空下来当是预备日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好好地休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天再在社团教室见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  作业完全没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月31日  暑假的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正怎么努力都不可能把作业做完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没法消除玩后的疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就这样子拖拖拉拉地过了懒散的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:00.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了  由它去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧  明天还要上学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关灯睡觉


